            "svg-code": "",
            "image_round": true,
            "text": "<p>I really can't say enough great things about Fenceworks! They always treat you with respect, honesty, and transparency. Regarding your next Fence project, look no further than \"The Guy on 41\"! I will be back this spring for Basketball Hoops, Trampolines, and Playgrounds... excited to complete my backyard with Fenceworks running the show!</p>",
