            "svg-code": "",
            "image_round": true,
            "text": "<p>I am so happy with the work that was completed. Fast, friendly, courteous, and honest.<br/>I had a beautiful fence built in my backyard and they worked so hard and quickly. I could not be happier and I will use them for any future projects.</p>",
            "name": "Brad Rooks",
            "source": "Google Reviews"
